HEADWORD: Dragonet
<hw>Drag"on*et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
little dragon.</def> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small British marine fish
(<gen>Callionymuslyra</gen>); -- called also <altname>yellow
sculpin</altname>, <altname>fox</altname>, and
<altname>gowdie</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dragonish</ent>⟦br⟧
